query:
SELECT 
  MIN(id) as min_id,
  MAX(id) as max_id,
  COUNT(*) as total
FROM clientes
WHERE projectId = 1 AND pesquisaId = 1;

-- Pegar 5 IDs reais
SELECT id, nome
FROM clientes
WHERE projectId = 1 AND pesquisaId = 1
ORDER BY id
LIMIT 5;
